# No local environment variables are required for login.
# Login uses the fixed user credentials stored in the app.
# For Amplify Gen 2, run `npx ampx sandbox` to generate amplify_outputs.json.
# The app will use that file automatically when present.
# You can also override the GraphQL endpoint manually:
# VITE_AWS_REGION=us-east-1
# VITE_AWS_APPSYNC_ENDPOINT=https://your-api-id.appsync-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/graphql
# VITE_AWS_APPSYNC_API_KEY=your-api-key
